title: Volleyball Top Five
text: Chap Carter & Mike Williams NCPrivateSchoolSports.com Providence Day School scored a huge win with a 3-2 thriller over former number one Covenant Day School. PD Chargers move into first place in the 3A Top Five and have a huge advantage going into the last part of the season. Next up for Providence Day is Charlotte Christian tomorrow and Cannon School next week. ... More ... To continue reading this article you must be a member. Sign Up Now!
